    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove employer National Insurance for all workers aged 16\u201325",
        "additional_details": "This could help boost the economy and get the young back to work or apprenticeships to allow the young to get working again and not leave a generation behind.",
        "background": "Removing employer National Insurance (NI) for all young workers could make it cheaper for businesses to hire them, potentially increasing entry-level jobs and apprenticeships. ",
